{"data":[{"id":564168776,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":307595822,"title":"高中生对哥德巴赫猜想的证明有哪些错误？","question_type":"normal","created":1546272354,"updated_time":1546301579,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"ddcb76fa8995876e8fc1007e6f9cc0ad","url_token":"bu-zheng-huang-nian","name":"不正荒年","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-0bac06f296bb594b57ad7fedf13a0ed8_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-0bac06f296bb594b57ad7fedf13a0ed8_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/ddcb76fa8995876e8fc1007e6f9cc0ad","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/564168776","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546337661,"updated_time":1546337661,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":5,"comment_count":7,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e我想说点别的，瓜是得吃，不过好像有点不好吃。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e他的知乎已经注销了，不知道会不会给他带来阴影。一大堆拿营销、吸粉说事的，是不是有些过分了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这个问题登上知乎榜首，被数万人关注，数千人在下面“回答”，有多少是在就事论事，又有多少是在嘲讽讽刺。回答的问题如果带有大量个人情绪，是否合适呢？大V小V也是公众人物，不是说在恶意相向，但过多的调侃是不是有点不合适？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不是说这个问题下存在“网络暴力”的回答，但是我实在不喜欢这种“球员空门不进，场馆的所有人对此唾沫横飞，恶语相向”的感觉。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ci\u003e知乎是网络问答社区，连接各行各业的用户，用户分享着彼此的知识、经验和见解。\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e知乎不是专门用来批判一个人的工具。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e“证明”是一个高中生，就说是吃着瓜的你们，喜欢这种被一群人唾沫星子压住的感觉吗？难道说这是罪有应得？罪在哪？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e他只是表达了他的观点，错了，然后承认了错误，这有什么问题吗？\u003c/b\u003e因为吸粉过多让你们觉得不甘心？因为语气太“狂”所以要好好修理一下？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e“要现实一点”？棱角分明的学生，这个年纪为什么要经历这样的事情——被公众吊起来批斗。难道这就是表达自己观点会得到的现实？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e在坐各位就没有青春年少时，一腔热血，总认为自己是正确的，批判万物的经历吗？不是要激励这种行为，但也不是一味地反对。至少不应该像现在这样冷嘲热讽啊。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我也是学生，也总有人在我耳边说：年轻人要现实一点。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e在这个年纪，我有兴趣，有毅力去做我喜欢的事情，我为什么不去做？\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"我想说点别的，瓜是得吃，不过好像有点不好吃。他的知乎已经注销了，不知道会不会给他带来阴影。一大堆拿营销、吸粉说事的，是不是有些过分了。这个问题登上知乎榜首，被数万人关注，数千人在下面“回答”，有多少是在就事论事，又有多少是在嘲讽讽刺。回答…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=218\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=216\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","totals":489}}
